{"search_data": "Uttar Pradesh[Yogi] UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana 2020 Registration / Application Form for Children of Labourers Uttar Pradesh Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana online application / registration form, launch date 12 june 2020, children of labourers in UP to get Rs. 1,000 (boys) & Rs. 1200 (girls) assistance amount, apply soon, students of class 8th, 9th, 10th will get an additional assistance of Rs. 6,000 per year, check complete details hereTable of Contents  Uttar Pradesh Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana 2020UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana Online Application / Registration FormIdentification of Children of LabourersAn Overview of UP Bal Shramik Vidya YojanaFrequently Asked Questions (FAQ\u2019s)Uttar Pradesh Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana 2020Uttar Pradesh government will launch a new scheme for children of labourers namely UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojna. In this scheme, the state govt. will provide monthly financial assistance to children of workers to stop them from working as child labourers and instead focus on their studies. Chief Minister Yogi Adityanath would launch the scheme on 12 June 2020 by sending funds to around 2,000 people.UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana Online Application / Registration FormLabour department will provide the assistance amount of Rs. 1,000 for boys and Rs. 1,200 to girls on monthly basis to labourer\u2019s children. Students of class 8th, 9th, 10th will get an additional assistance of Rs. 6,000 per year. As per the initial reports, there would be conditional cash transfer for child labourers. Moreover, UP govt. will provide higher amount to girls to aid their studies and to keep them away from work.The online applications for the UP Labourers Children Education Scheme may be invited at the official UP government website or at a new dedicated portal. As soon as the UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana online application / registration form filling process begins, we will update it here.Identification of Children of LabourersWhile online applications for UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana would be invited online at a later date, the task of identification of such children of labourers has now been given to the labour department. The UP Labour Department will manage the UP Child Labourers Education Scheme and its beneficiaries. This scheme is important as UP is reportedly among those states which have high number of child labour related cases. Thus, the Yogi Adityanath led UP government has decided that cash transfer under the new schem would be conditional i.e given only when set conditions are met.\u0905\u0925\u0935\u093e \u0926\u094b\u0928\u094b\u0902 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0938\u0947 \u0915\u094b\u0908 \u090f\u0915 \u0915\u093f\u0938\u0940 \u0905\u0938\u093e\u0927\u094d\u092f \u092c\u0940\u092e\u093e\u0930\u0940 \u0938\u0947 \u0917\u094d\u0930\u0938\u093f\u0924 \u0939\u0948, \u092f\u093e \u0905\u0928\u094d\u092f \u092a\u0930\u093f\u0938\u094d\u0925\u093f\u0924\u093f\u092f\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0915\u093e\u0930\u0923 \u0909\u0928\u094d\u0939\u0947\u0902 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u092a\u0930\u093f\u0935\u093e\u0930 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f \u0915\u093e\u0930\u094d\u092f \u0915\u0930\u0928\u093e \u092a\u0921\u093c\u0924\u093e \u0925\u093e\u0964 \u0910\u0938\u0947 \u092c\u091a\u094d\u091a\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f \u0906\u091c \u090f\u0915 \u0928\u0908 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u2018\u092c\u093e\u0932 \u0936\u094d\u0930\u092e\u093f\u0915 \u0935\u093f\u0926\u094d\u092f\u093e \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e\u2019 \u0909\u0924\u094d\u0924\u0930 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0926\u0947\u0936 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u093e\u0930\u092e\u094d\u092d \u0915\u0940 \u091c\u093e \u0930\u0939\u0940 \u0939\u0948: \u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0936\u094d\u0930\u0940 @myogiadityanath \u091c\u0940\u2014 CM Office, GoUP (@CMOfficeUP) June 12, 2020 The UP state govt. has set a target to roll-out phase wise employment programme for labourers in the state by 15 June 2020. Yogi Adityanath has directed divisional commissioners to review the development work in the districts to check progress made until the COVID-19 lockdown. These officials will also check how much work is remaining in each district. District magistrates will then be directed to prepare a plan to get these works completed on priority basis.CM has also given directions that development schemes of the Centre and the state government should be implemented on one hand while providing employment to labourers and workers on the other hand. This would help in \u201cnavnirman (reconstruction)\u201d of the entire Uttar Pradesh state.\u0939\u0930 \u092c\u091a\u094d\u091a\u0947 \u0915\u094b \u0909\u0938\u0915\u0940 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093f\u092d\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0905\u0928\u0941\u0930\u0942\u092a \u0909\u0928\u094d\u0928\u0924\u093f \u0915\u0947 \u0905\u0935\u0938\u0930 \u0909\u092a\u0932\u092c\u094d\u0927 \u0915\u0930\u093e\u0928\u0947 \u0939\u0947\u0924\u0941 \u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0936\u094d\u0930\u0940 @myogiadityanath \u091c\u0940 \u0915\u0943\u0924\u0938\u0902\u0915\u0932\u094d\u092a\u093f\u0924 \u0939\u0948\u0902\u0964\u092c\u093e\u0932 \u0939\u093f\u0924\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0938\u0902\u0930\u0915\u094d\u0937\u0923 \u0915\u0947 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u092f\u093e\u0938\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0915\u094d\u0930\u092e \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0906\u091c \u0905\u0902\u0924\u0930\u0930\u093e\u0937\u094d\u091f\u094d\u0930\u0940\u092f \u092c\u093e\u0932 \u0936\u094d\u0930\u092e \u0928\u093f\u0937\u0947\u0927 \u0926\u093f\u0935\u0938 \u0915\u0947 \u0905\u0935\u0938\u0930 \u092a\u0930 \u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u091c\u0940 \u0928\u0947 '\u092c\u093e\u0932 \u0936\u094d\u0930\u092e\u093f\u0915 \u0935\u093f\u0926\u094d\u092f\u093e \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e' \u0915\u093e \u0932\u094b\u0915\u093e\u0930\u094d\u092a\u0923 \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e\u0964 pic.twitter.com/dZHBVKqpAB\u2014 CM Office, GoUP (@CMOfficeUP) June 12, 2020 An Overview of UP Bal Shramik Vidya YojanaHere are the highlights of the UP education scheme for children of labourers:-Name of SchemeBal Shramik Vidya YojanaBeneficiariesOrphans & Children of LabourersType of ArticleApplication / Registration FormState NameUttar PradeshLaunch Date12 June 2020To be Launched byYogi AdityanathPurposeProviding monthly financial assistance to enable beneficiaries in their studies and prevent child labourAssistance AmountRs. 1,000 for boys & Rs. 1200 for girls, additional assistance of Rs. 6,000 p.a to class 8th, 9th and 10th studentsHow to ApplyOnline at New Portal (to be launched)Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ\u2019s)Here are the most frequently asked questions about the new scheme:-1. What is UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojana ? In this UP Bal Shramik Vidya Yojna, govt. will provide monthly financial assistance to educate orphans and children of labourers.2. Who will Launch the UP Bal Shramik Vidya Scheme and When ? As per the official sources, Chief Minister Yogi Adityanath will launch this Bal Shramik Vidya Yojna on 12 June 2020 (Launch Date).3. Does this Child Labourers Welfare Scheme requires Registration ? As per the reports, the new Bal Shramik Vidya Yojna will require candidates to apply through online mode at a new dedicated portal or at the UP govt\u2019s official website. Applicants will have to fill UP Bal Shramik Education Scheme online application / registration form to get its benefits.4. What will be the Benefits or Assistance Amount under this scheme ? Each boy will get Rs. 1,000 per month and each girl will receive Rs. 1,200 per month to pursue their studies and not get indulged in any type of child labour related works. Students of class 8th, 9th, 10th will get an additional assistance of Rs. 6,000 per year.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/lucknow/up-cm-to-launch-financial-scheme-for-children-of-labourers-today-6454912